de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.jrdf2vec.walk_generators.parsers

Class NtMemoryParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.jrdf2vec.walk_generators.parsers.MemoryParser
      • de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.jrdf2vec.walk_generators.parsers.NtMemoryParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IParser

    public class NtMemoryParser
extends MemoryParser
    A parser for NT files. Mainly implemented to support MemoryParser.getRandomTripleForSubject(String) in an efficient way.

    • Nested Class Summary

      (package private) class  NtMemoryParser.FileReaderThread
